ca.gedge.opgraph.extensions
Interface CustomProcessing

All Known Implementing Classes:
ForEachNode, MacroNode
public interface CustomProcessing

An extension meant for any OpNode that requires custom initialization, operation, and termination when being stepped into by a CustomProcessing.CustomProcessor. CustomProcessing.CustomProcessor will only step into a node with a CompositeNode extension. For example, a macro node may need to map inputs from the macro node's OpContext to appropriate nodes on initialization, and map outputs from nodes to its OpContext on termination.
